dcterms:description: A dataset for zero-shot learning consisting of 50 animal classes, with a total of 37,322 images and an average of 746 images per class. The dataset is used for evaluating unsupervised open domain recognition.

dcterms:description: A large-scale dataset for visual learning and understanding from web data, consisting of 1,000 classes with a total of 1,279,847 images. The target domain is the validation set of WebVision, which contains 5,000 classes and 294,009 images.
dcterms:title: I2WebV
